'desc': [u'

Farlin Fish Nail Clipper Price: Rs.297

Infant’s nails are soft but they still have to be trimmed to avoid dirt accumulation and to prevent the child from hurting himself. The Safety Scissors or the Fish Nail Clipper from Farlin is an adorable nail trimmer that comes in the shape of a fish. This Nail Clipper has a special design that allows you to collect the nails as you clip them. This feature will help you in preventing clipped nails getting shattered all over the place. There is a nail buff at the bottom of this Farlin Nail Clipper with which you can easily and effectively polish the rough edges of the nails. Make sure you buff the nails to prevent sharp and rough edges that can hurt your bundle of joy.

This Farlin Fish Nail Clipper comes with an anti-skid design that will keep the clipper firmly in your hand without slipping. The plastic used on the body of this Nail Clipper from Farlin is non-toxic. The small blades used in this Nail clipper let you watch the nails clearly and hence reduces the chances of bruising your infant’s fingers.

'desc': [u'

Farlin Baby Walker (Orange) Price: Rs.4250

Key Features

  • Dual Function Option
  • Comfortable Seating Facility
  • Walker can be Adjusted into Five Different Positions
  • Baby Walk Independently and also Comprises of a Sound Play Tray

If you are a multitasking parent and you are on the lookout for a compact and safe to use walker for your baby
column13:
this Farlin Baby Walker would be the right pick. This walker would not only let you do your chores without having to take much tension but would also keep your little one happy and occupied. This walker from Farlin is ideal for use by both boys and girls.

\r\n

\r\n\tIn addition to this
column14: the height of the walker can be adjusted into five different positions while in use. This feature offers ultimate care and comfort for your little one while walking. In order to facilitate smooth and hassle-free strolling
column15: this Farlin Baby Walker is equipped with a wheeled bottom. Designed with a <strong>comfortable seating facility
column16:
this walker lets your baby enjoy its everyday strolls to the fullest.

\r\n

\r\n\tThis Farlin Baby Walker not only lets your baby walk independently but also comprises of a sound play tray that keeps your little one occupied even while you are not around. Also
column17:
the walker comes with a dual function option. Your little one would certainly love moving around in this smartly designed Farlin Baby Walker. You could now stop fretting about not being able to complete your daily tasks. All you need to do is place your little one in this Farlin Baby Walker and watch your baby walk around safe and secure.

\n
\n ']
